  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bc1 \u0b93\u0baf\u0bbe \u0baa\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bb3 \u0b95\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbe \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Recovery of Kerala Ganja from a closed hostel in Battulu Oya area",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kerala Ganja hidden in a closed hostel in Battulu Oya area of \u200b\u200bPuttalam has been seized.",
        "9 kg packs of Kerala Ganja, which were hidden in a closed hotel in Battulu Oya area of \u200b\u200bMundal Police Division, were seized today (21) afternoon.",
        "The police said that the ganja packs were seized during a search operation in the said hotel based on the confidential information received by the crime branch of the police that it was hidden in a hotel.",
        "Munthal Police said that no one has been arrested on suspicion and they are continuing to investigate the matter."
      ],
